                </div>
                <div class="opportunities_news_slider__slide">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553729459-efe14ef6055d?w=1200&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Kredi Haberi 2" />
                    <div class="opportunities_news_slider__content">
                        <h3>İhtiyaç Kredisi Faizleri Düştü</h3>
